    {
      "id": "beat-8",
      "kind": "comparison",
      "title": "Before and After Requests",
      "narration": "Let's see the difference between doing web requests without Requests and with it. Without Requests, you'd have to manually handle URL encoding, form data, and SSL verification. With Requests, it's all automated. You just write simple Python code to send your requests and get the data you need.",
